name: GSC X Lady Killer M. Fox Tee Red
description: Gimmick is proudly setting a series of t-shirts  called "Homage" to pay respect to many company's in which have influenced Gimmick Skate Co. This specific tee honors Diamond's Sade Tee, but with our own twist. The beautiful Megan fox makes a silhouette on a carefully designed Gimmick T-shirt. 1 of 3. Be on the lookout for the next set in the "Homage" series.

name: Prince Infected Icons Purple
description:
Gimmick Skate Co X Killer Napkins Collab Release, the first of the "Infected Icon's" Series.

From the twisted minds of GSC & Killer napkins, we bring you the zombie formerly known as prince.

This Tee Is SUPER limited to 150 pieces, the shirt will come with a hand signed certificate _/150 and a GSC sticker!

The first 75 will be a limited online release!

The industry is filled with gimmicks, not only is this skate brand about exclusivity, it's about unity in the skate community.
Most brands are gimmick's in their own right, but Gimmick Skate Co is about more than just the outrageous gimmicks and graphics on our products. Gimmick is owned by true skateboarder's with a heart of gold, made for skateboarder's and anyone who respects the skate culture.


6 oz. 100% Cotton Tubular Jersey.* Double-needle bottom hem and sleeves. Shoulder-to-shoulder tape. Preshrunk to minimize shrinkage. Body Width: S=18", M=20", L=22", XL=24", 2XL=26"
